text: Sissie Luo (born March 5, 2001) is a Guamanian beauty pageant titleholder who won Miss Universe Guam 2019. Luo will now represent Guam at the Miss Universe 2019 pageant. == Personal life == She was born and raised at the village of Tamuning, Guam. She is of Chinese descent and she can speak Mandarin and English. She is a recent graduate of Saint John's High School. == Pageantry == === Miss Universe Guam 2019 === Luo began her pageantry career representing Tamuning in the Miss Universe Guam 2019 pageant. She won and took home three special awards; Best In Swimsuit, Best In Long Gown and Miss Photogenic. She succeeded outgoing Miss Universe Guam 2018 Athena McNinch. === Miss Universe 2019 === As Miss Universe Guam 2019, Luo has obtained the right to represent Guam in Miss Universe 2019 Pageant later this year. ==References== Category:Miss Universe 2019 contestants Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:People from Tamuning, Guam Category:Guamanian people of Chinese descent
